{"word":"G1601 - ἐκπίπτω - ekpíptō - ek-pip'-to - Be cast","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκπίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekpíptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-pip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be cast</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விழு, அவமாய் போ, உதிர், ஒழி"},{"paragraph":"to fall out of, to fall down from, to perish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>; to <i>drop away</i>; specifically <i>be driven out</i> of one&rsquo;s course; figuratively to <i>lose</i>, <i>become inefficient:</i> - be cast, fail, fall (away, off), take none effect.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1601/1601\">G1601</a>, <a href=\"#/G2667/2667\">G2667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3895/3895\">G3895</a>, <a href=\"#/G3900/3900\">G3900</a>, <a href=\"#/G4045/4045\">G4045</a>, <a href=\"#/G4098/4098\">G4098</a>, <a href=\"#/G4430/4430\">G4430</a>, <a href=\"#/G4431/4431\">G4431</a>"}]}